rows.name: PSM-root-policy-compartments
statements: allow service PSM to manage all-resources in compartment managedcompartmentforpaas
allow service OracleEnterpriseManager to manage all-resources in compartment managedcompartmentforpaas
allow service PSM to manage users in tenancy where target.user.name = /__PSM*/
allow any-user to manage all-resources in compartment managedcompartmentforpaas where request.user.name = /__PSM*/

allow any-user to manage all-resources in compartment managedcompartmentforpaas where request.instance.compartment.id = 'ocid1.compartment.oc1..aaaaaaaah2fxitwrxzp5ciu2pmhyfzpc6rwdeurfvyjzmzg7l5cypt5agnkq'
allow service PSM to inspect tenant in tenancy
allow service PSM to inspect compartments in tenancy
rows.title: PSM-root-policy-compartments

rows.description: Temporary policy for /bootstrapDefaultDomain API's whitelisted services. Gives access to IAM work request APIs and ability to delete these policy when access is no longer needed.
rows.name: BootstrapProvisioning
statements: ALLOW SERVICE tenancylifecycleservice to {IAM_WORKREQUEST_READ, IAM_WORKREQUEST_INSPECT} IN TENANCY
ALLOW SERVICE tenancylifecycleservice to {POLICY_DELETE} IN TENANCY where target.policy.name='BootstrapProvisioning'
rows.title: BootstrapProvisioning

rows.name: PSM-mgd-comp-policy
statements: allow any-user to read all-resources in compartment managedcompartmentforpaas
allow service PSM to manage all-resources in compartment managedcompartmentforpaas
allow any-user to manage virtual-network-family in compartment managedcompartmentforpaas where all { target.vcn.display-name != /mgmt-vcn*/, request.operation != 'CreateVcn' }
allow any-user to use buckets in compartment managedcompartmentforpaas where request.instance.compartment.id = 'ocid1.compartment.oc1..aaaaaaaah2fxitwrxzp5ciu2pmhyfzpc6rwdeurfvyjzmzg7l5cypt5agnkq'
allow any-user to use objects in compartment managedcompartmentforpaas where request.instance.compartment.id = 'ocid1.compartment.oc1..aaaaaaaah2fxitwrxzp5ciu2pmhyfzpc6rwdeurfvyjzmzg7l5cypt5agnkq'
allow group Administrators to manage instance-console-connection in compartment managedcompartmentforpaas
allow group Administrators to manage volume-backups in compartment managedcompartmentforpaas
allow group Administrators to manage boot-volume-backups in compartment managedcompartmentforpaas
allow group Administrators to manage backup-policies in compartment managedcompartmentforpaas
allow group Administrators to manage backup-policy-assignments in compartment managedcompartmentforpaas

allow group Administrators to manage volumes in compartment managedcompartmentforpaas where any {request.operation='CreateVolumeBackupPolicyAssignment', request.operation='DeleteVolumeBackupPolicyAssignment'}

allow group Administrators to manage volumes in compartment managedcompartmentforpaas where any {request.operation='CreateVolumeBackup', request.operation='DeleteVolumeBackup', request.operation='CreateBootVolumeBackup', request.operation='DeleteBootVolumeBackup'}
allow resource psmrp psm to manage all-resources in compartment managedcompartmentforpaas
rows.title: PSM-mgd-comp-policy

rows.name: Tenant Admin Policy
statements: ALLOW GROUP Administrators to manage all-resources IN TENANCY
rows.title: Tenant Admin Policy

rows.description: Policy to enable marketplace services on the tenancy
rows.name: MarketplaceServicePolicy
statements: ALLOW SERVICE marketplace to manage App-catalog-publisher-listing IN TENANCY
ALLOW SERVICE marketplace to read tenant IN TENANCY
ALLOW SERVICE marketplace to read compartments IN TENANCY
ALLOW SERVICE marketplace to read instance-images IN TENANCY
ALLOW SERVICE marketplace to inspect instances IN TENANCY
ALLOW SERVICE marketplace to read orm-stacks IN TENANCY
ALLOW SERVICE marketplace to read orm-jobs IN TENANCY
rows.title: MarketplaceServicePolicy

rows.name: SecurityAudit
statements: Allow group SecurityAudit to read all-resources in tenancy
rows.title: SecurityAudit

rows.description: The namespace for the automatic tags.
rows.name: Oracle-Tags
rows.title: Oracle-Tags
